Results:  This command is a useful, conenient way to look at the users.
          The users on the list will fall into 4 categories based on idle
          time. They are..

          Active:    Users that are idle less than 3 minutes.
          Awake:     Users that are idle 3 minutes to 60 minutes.
          Idle:      Users that are idle 60 minutes to 3 hours (180 min.)
          Comatose:  Users idle more than 3 hours.

          This also shows number of users connected and invis users,
          following the conditions of the normal .who command.

See also: who